{
  "id": "2657631070_1",
  "title": "一位语言学博士的跨界“琴缘”",
  "content": "<div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content autoTypeSetting24psection\" id=\"js_content\">\n <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 0px 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"510147409\" data-ratio=\"0.30919765166340507\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"511\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/OD7oJvxOf6ZCMtECMvc55vp7Dvg8deeuXyrzX5zOxsX4I30RlTGQ9xohWcqMvzIRcbdLEGgABl591Ikx8gVFiaQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"/>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;width: 100%;border-style: dashed;border-width: 1px;border-color: rgba(0, 13, 43, 0.15);height: auto;align-self: flex-start;padding: 6px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section style=\"justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"margin: 10px 0% 13px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <section style=\"color: rgb(62, 62, 62);text-align: justify;padding: 0px 17px;font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1.5px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">\n        世纪之交的深圳超市中，13岁的吴芸莉随手拿起一支20元的竹笛。从未接触过竹笛，她竟流畅地吹出了完整的曲调。\n       </span>\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">\n        <br/>\n       </span>\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">\n        如今，已是江苏大学文学院教师的吴芸莉，左手抚古琴，右手握书卷。她的故事，是天赋与坚持的写照，更是中华优秀传统文化薪火相传的佳话。\n       </span>\n      </p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0.5em 0px;padding-left: 0.5em;padding-right: 0.5em;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;width: 100%;box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) 0.2em 0.2em 0.5em;height: auto !important;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-color: white;\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"510147411\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OD7oJvxOf6ZCMtECMvc55vp7Dvg8deeu9FccUjNZqBAeJZ9mDs9Ujtou1NOWicZoU1aAicBVQWqPdibMr6zxQCdcA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"/>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(126, 127, 123);letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">\n      吴芸莉在弹奏古琴\n     </span>\n    </strong>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 20px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;background-color: rgba(230, 223, 189, 0.54);min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;padding: 0px 21px;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: -10px 0px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px;border-color: rgb(202, 186, 132);padding: 6px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 2.5;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(166, 149, 88);width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <span leaf=\"\">\n           天赋初显：笛声中无心插柳\n          </span>\n         </strong>\n        </p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1.5px;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     吴芸莉的音乐启蒙始于90年代初。小学音乐老师发现了她出色的音准与节奏感，破例让她使用学校唯一的钢琴，并利用课余时间义务教授弹琴和乐理。“我的乐理知识基本都是小学音乐老师教的。”吴芸莉坦言，这段启蒙为她打下了良好的基础。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0.5em 0px;padding-left: 0.5em;padding-right: 0.5em;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;width: 100%;box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) 0.2em 0.2em 0.5em;height: auto !important;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-color: white;\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"510147410\" data-ratio=\"0.6703703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OD7oJvxOf6ZCMtECMvc55vp7Dvg8deeu4rqibAPPYrIMrFWQUvhnicgGv2CbZw1UXoiabREiaicFTIJIr5picFnDtqHQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"/>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(126, 127, 123);letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">\n      吴芸莉在一次演出中吹奏竹笛\n     </span>\n    </strong>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1.5px;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     随家从江西小城迁至深圳，在初中一次文艺汇演上，学姐的笛声让原本学习圆号的吴芸莉深深着迷。没有教材，无人指导，吴芸莉用零花钱买教材钻研；没有乐器，便以笔代笛，练习指法。直至13岁在超市的那次“无心插柳”，家人才真正看到她在民乐上的天赋与热爱。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     <br/>\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     随后，吴芸莉积极寻找专业老师，踏上竹笛和箫的学习之路。高中住校时，吹笛吹箫成了她释放压力的方式，也成了宿舍楼里同学期待的慰藉。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 20px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;background-color: rgba(230, 223, 189, 0.54);min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;padding: 0px 21px;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: -10px 0px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px;border-color: rgb(202, 186, 132);padding: 6px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 2.5;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(166, 149, 88);width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <span leaf=\"\">\n           古琴“开窍”：北大学海遇知音\n          </span>\n         </strong>\n        </p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1.5px;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     大学期间，吴芸莉展现出对民族乐器的广泛兴趣和快速学习能力，系统学习了古筝、琵琶并达到较高的演奏水平。最初接触古琴时，她却觉得“很难听”。老师告诉她，古琴底蕴深厚，需要文化修养支撑。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     <br/>\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     进入北京大学中文系攻读语言学硕博期间，吴芸莉与古琴再续前缘。“古琴很难吗？我就想试试。”吴芸莉认为，当初觉得难听，或许是自己“国学底蕴”不够，如今在中文系深造，她觉得自己“够格”了。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0.5em 0px;padding-left: 0.5em;padding-right: 0.5em;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;width: 100%;box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) 0.2em 0.2em 0.5em;height: auto !important;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-color: white;\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"510147413\" data-ratio=\"0.6768518518518518\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OD7oJvxOf6ZCMtECMvc55vp7Dvg8deeuVd203g15W0aoBgxkJWXhkg2xicsictttVa1y6shgZsVeXDvOIlv9hQ8A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"/>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(126, 127, 123);letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">\n      吴芸莉（右一）给学生上古琴课\n     </span>\n    </strong>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1.5px;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     吴芸莉找到北大“文一琴馆”的黄文懿老师，当《梅花三弄》的琴音流淌而出，曾经“沉闷难听”的声音却有了别样的韵味。为了兼顾学业与琴艺，她开启了“双轨”生活：每天清晨七点琴馆练琴，下午两点图书馆钻研学业。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     <br/>\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     “音乐学院的学生都没你刻苦。”惜才的黄文懿倾囊相授，并带她登上舞台，与音乐学院科班生同台演出。“音乐早已超越了爱好，成为我生命中不可或缺的力量源泉。”吴芸莉说。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 20px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;background-color: rgba(230, 223, 189, 0.54);min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;padding: 0px 21px;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: -10px 0px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px;border-color: rgb(202, 186, 132);padding: 6px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 2.5;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(166, 149, 88);width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <span leaf=\"\">\n           大师点醒：古琴当归文脉\n          </span>\n         </strong>\n        </p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1.5px;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     2017年，聆听首批国家级古琴非遗传承人姚公白的演奏会，成为吴芸莉认知的分水岭。“那不仅是旋律，更是境像。”那种“人乐合一”的至高境界，让吴芸莉领悟到，弹琴的真谛不仅在于“好听”，更在于“入境”。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     <br/>\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     当姚公白海选学员教授古曲《阳春》《流水》时，吴芸莉凭借过人天赋，仅用七天就完成识谱、练习，成功入选。要知道，仅根据这两首曲子的减字谱弹出基本音调，常人通常需数月之功。她的悟性给姚公白留下深刻印象，后来得以赴香港继续随其深造。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0.5em 0px;padding-left: 0.5em;padding-right: 0.5em;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;width: 100%;box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) 0.2em 0.2em 0.5em;height: auto !important;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-color: white;\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"510147412\" data-ratio=\"0.5685185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OD7oJvxOf6ZCMtECMvc55vp7Dvg8deeuKibOJ1PDTgD0k52iahzakGcl7UjCia3Hm9RvLiacgibIBKTV2SLicGDk446g/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"/>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(126, 127, 123);letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">\n      吴芸莉（中）给学生上古琴课\n     </span>\n    </strong>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1.5px;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     探索古琴古谱的过程中，吴芸莉体悟到谱字、语言规律与传统文化间的深层联系。一次，姚公白对她说：“古琴很适合开在中文系。”这句话点醒了吴芸莉，也坚定了她在文学院传承古琴的信念。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 20px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;background-color: rgba(230, 223, 189, 0.54);min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <section style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;height: auto;padding: 0px 21px;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <section style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: -10px 0px;width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px;border-color: rgb(202, 186, 132);padding: 6px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <section style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 2.5;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(166, 149, 88);width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n         <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n          <span leaf=\"\">\n           弦歌不辍：三尺讲台传清音\n          </span>\n         </strong>\n        </p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1.5px;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     博士后工作结束，吴芸莉来到江苏大学文学院任教，讲授本科生“现代汉语”必修课、“语言、逻辑与语义”选修课，研究生“中华文化与才艺展示”选修课，以及留学生“高级综合汉语”必修课等。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     <br/>\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     教学之余，吴芸莉依托学院“江南文化传播中心”，创建了“古琴传习室”。起初通过讲座吸引大一学生，后借助“中华才艺训练”必修实践课推广并筛选学员。目前，“古琴传习室”已有三届学员，每届5人左右。“有人爱听我就弹，有人愿学我就教。”吴芸莉说。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0.5em 0px;padding-left: 0.5em;padding-right: 0.5em;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;width: 100%;box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) 0.2em 0.2em 0.5em;height: auto !important;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-color: white;\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"510147417\" data-ratio=\"0.6342592592592593\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OD7oJvxOf6ZCMtECMvc55vp7Dvg8deeuhMRXxhTibAL5XcMKl2Eydib1cdLolfa4VqQMdQfEd2cVXy44MQ4gHZiag/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"/>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(126, 127, 123);letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">\n      吴芸莉（前排中）和中外学生留影\n     </span>\n    </strong>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1.5px;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     面对学生流动性大、课业重、古琴数量有限等问题，吴芸莉优化策略，实行分层教学，将资源留给真正热爱的学生。“方法教了，关键看学生是否愿意学和练。”即便是短短三周的必修课，她也力求学生能辨音色、弹简单曲调、懂基础乐理、增强节奏感。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     <br/>\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     文学院21级学生戴张力入学时零基础，在吴芸莉的指导下勤学苦练，甚至自购古琴假期练习。毕业时，他已成为传习室的“台柱子”：“感谢吴老师让我爱上古琴，毕业后我也会继续学。”\n    </span>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0.5em 0px;padding-left: 0.5em;padding-right: 0.5em;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;width: 100%;box-shadow: rgb(102, 102, 102) 0.2em 0.2em 0.5em;height: auto !important;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;border-color: white;\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"510147416\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OD7oJvxOf6ZCMtECMvc55vp7Dvg8deeu2l0dEqC0Nr3f6ewqgtIhMGNVq4J2iauJ0ZFXleE7LNiajcxdS1GrZ3tg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"/>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(126, 127, 123);letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">\n      吴芸莉（右一）给老师们上古琴课\n     </span>\n    </strong>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 1.5px;padding: 0px 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     吴芸莉的热情也感染了同事，文学院院长任晓霏，教师黄雪云、王丽媛，图书馆老师骆雪松等都在她的带动下开始习琴。“三年来，古琴传习室面向中外师生奏响清音，琴韵回荡校园，更成为连接东西方文化的桥梁。”任晓霏说。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     <br/>\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     古琴之于吴芸莉，是音乐，亦是快乐。站在讲台与琴桌前，吴芸莉继续着“弦外人生”，左手琴弦，右手书卷，弦歌不辍，传承千年文脉。\n    </span>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 60%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"510147414\" data-ratio=\"0.2\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"svg\" data-w=\"300\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_svg/BA8GZZ2EGwUvX397zcBAYdJBWIjYaUe6NrqaROWgd45Ecx5FHXadfU3SyHiaey2yMHm4BTjqKwteKk88nKY8iaGewCftic88qiaI/640?wx_fmt=svg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;height: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"/>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">\n    <br/>\n   </span>\n  </p>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 2;color: rgb(126, 127, 123);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     审核｜吴奕\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     统筹｜杨雨\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     编辑｜杨雨\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     文字｜郑礼月\n    </span>\n   </p>\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     图片｜郑礼月 部分由本人提供\n    </span>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"510147418\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OD7oJvxOf6ZCMtECMvc55vp7Dvg8deeuEBu1Wibz6qFY4tMiapCgMMibiaXcMbkQNG9nE9ljyFV4E8pp9QCfL06cdw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"/>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\">\n     <br/>\n    </span>\n   </p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin: 0px 0%;text-align: right;transform: translate3d(-30px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-30px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-30px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-30px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n   <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <section style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;padding-left: 5px;padding-right: 5px;line-height: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 2px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">\n        爱江大，请\n       </span>\n       <span style=\"color: rgba(175, 27, 2, 0.97);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\">\n         点亮\n        </span>\n       </span>\n      </strong>\n     </p>\n    </section>\n    <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;display: inline-block;vertical-align: bottom;line-height: 0;width: 12%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"510147415\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"196\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/OD7oJvxOf6ZCMtECMvc55vp7Dvg8deeuiasxLyj7md2J3nbaLqHLQGTcIfC8q7vzFtMkYkO2YQpv7vWXpoS4ZSg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\"/>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n </section>\n <p style=\"display: none;\">\n  <mp-style-type data-value=\"3\">\n  </mp-style-type>\n </p>\n</div>\n",
